name: $$$ NARCISSIST
description: Falling in love with the reflection of his Old Money, the $$$ Narcissist stares at the face of wealth reflected back at him. He realises too late that he loves Old Money far too much. An endless loop of $$$.
collection_description: SuperRare makes it easy to create, sell, and collect rare digital art.
